1. *Posebno* se divio njenom nesebičnom delu. (He particularly admired her selfless work.)
2. On je navikao da zahteva *posebno*. (He was used to demanding something special.)
3. Svi smo imali *posebna* osećanja prema njoj. (We all had special feelings towards her.)
4. Imamo *posebnu* želju da pomognemo. (We have a special desire to help.)
5. Imamo *posebnu* pažnju i poštovanje prema našim starijim. (We have a special attention and respect towards our elders.)